<P>
   NEW YORK (AP) -- Prices moved higher in early trading on Wall
Street on Thursday, led by another advance in tech stocks as
Microsoft shares rose on a report that the company is moving closer
to resolving its antitrust dispute with the government.
</P>
<P>
   In the first hour of trading on Wall Street, the Dow Jones
