Meisterstuck Solitaire stainless-steel ballpoint pen, a $185
Baccarat crystal heart, $59 Wolford Stay-Hip Sheer Tight bodywear,
$38 Wolford cotton knee socks, Godiva chocolates and a bottle of
Absolut Mandrin vodka.
